<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I dont remember if he casts spells, but i know that he Harm Touches, for around 380 dmg to open fight.  A good tactic is to have SK in group make a pet, and have the pet attack the AoF to absorb the HT.  Make sure you keep trying to snare or root, he like to resist it often, cause if he gets away from you, he has extremely bad pathing and will teleport away (through a pathing bug) and come back fully healed.</font></td></tr></table>
